    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0839a20"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>婺州金華山<persName key="A012606">神暄</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0839a21"/><persName key="A012606">釋神暄</persName>，俗姓留，<placeName key="PL000000018363">建陽</placeName>人也。幼而沈靜，非問不<lb
ed="T" n="0839a22"/>言。客遊<placeName key="PL000000013517">婺女</placeName>，入開元寺<!--找不到此地-->，志願出家焉。無<lb
ed="T" n="0839a23"/>何，本郡太守入寺訪其師，見<persName key="A012606">暄</persName>神彩朗練。<lb
ed="T" n="0839a24"/>太守善相人也，顧之數四，且曰：「<persName key="A012606">是子</persName>真出<lb
ed="T" n="0839a25"/>塵之器，異日承受深法，千眾圍遶，必超上<lb
ed="T" n="0839a26"/>果，非凡氣也。」乃誦七佛俱胝神呪，昏曉不<lb
ed="T" n="0839a27"/>絕。納戒畢，於<placeName key="PL000000013486">金華山</placeName>北洞，<placeName key="PL000000013492">百家巖</placeName>有石穴，<lb
ed="T" n="0839a28"/><persName key="A012606">暄</persName>居中止息，不構庵室，作露地頭陀，復無<lb
ed="T" n="0839a29"/>床榻。然有神人吐紫色雲氣而高覆之。遐<pb ed="T" n="0839b" xml:id="T50.2061.0839b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0839b01"/>望冉冉，猶獨柱觀焉。其神人時來問道，拱<lb
ed="T" n="0839b02"/>手白<persName key="A012606">暄</persName>曰：「<placeName key="PL000000013493">赤松洞</placeName>之東峯有林泉卓異，<persName key="A012606">師</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0839b03"/>可居之否？」<persName key="A012606">暄</persName>隨請往住，數年越多徵瑞。<date from-iso="0786-02-08" key="j20081792008532" to-iso="0787-01-27">貞<lb
ed="T" n="0839b04"/>元二年</date>遇<persName key="A010282">志賢禪師</persName>，問<persName key="A012606">暄</persName>如此持誦，魔事<lb
ed="T" n="0839b05"/>必生。欲滅魔怨，須識身本。身本既真，無魔<lb
ed="T" n="0839b06"/>無佛，豁然開悟，理事俱成，神呪功倍。<date from-iso="0813-02-09" key="j20180422018395" to-iso="0814-01-28">元和八<lb
ed="T" n="0839b07"/>年</date>，<persName key="A012611">范敭</persName>中丞知仰，遣使齎乳香氈罽器<anchor xml:id="beg0839001"/>皿<anchor xml:id="end0839001"/><lb
ed="T" n="0839b08"/>施<persName key="A012606">暄</persName>，並迴施現前大眾。次中書舍人<persName key="A012612">王仲</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0839b09"/>請於大雲寺<!--找不到此地-->為眾受菩薩戒。<date from-iso="0817-01-25" key="j20194882019871" to-iso="0818-02-12">十二載</date>，<placeName key="PL000000022160">平昌</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0839b10"/><persName key="A009184">孟簡</persName>尚書自<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName>甄請，不赴。<date from-iso="0817-08-20" key="j20196952019724" to-iso="0817-09-18">八月</date>，俄迴<placeName key="PL000000013486">舊<lb
ed="T" n="0839b11"/>山</placeName>，人莫詳測。倏云示滅，春秋七十六。弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0839b12"/>建塔焉。一云<persName key="A012606">暄</persName>在<placeName key="PL000000013486">金華山</placeName>北，多寒少陽。神<lb
ed="T" n="0839b13"/>人問曰：「<persName key="A012606">師</persName>須何物？」曰：「<persName key="A012606">吾</persName>在<placeName key="PL000000013486">山</placeName>之陰，苦於凜<lb
ed="T" n="0839b14"/>冽」神曰：「小事耳。」至夜聞暄闐之聲，明旦見<lb
ed="T" n="0839b15"/>一小峯移矣。</p>
